HOSEA

HOSEA

 

 

Penulis: Hosea (1:1).

Author: Hosea (1:1).

 

 

Waktu Ministrinya: Satu periode sekitar enam puluh tahun, kira-kira sejak tahun 785 SM, selama pemerintahan Uzia (Azarya), raja Yehuda, sampai kira-kira 725 SM, selama pemerintahan Hizkia, raja Yehuda (1:1).

Time of His Ministry: A period of about sixty years, from approximately 785 B.C., during the reign of Uzziah (Azariah), king of Judah, to approximately 725 B.C., during the reign of Hezekiah, king of Judah (1:1).

 

 

Tempat Ministrinya: Kerajaan Israel di utara.

Place of His Ministry: The northern kingdom of Israel.

 

 

Sasaran Ministrinya: Kerajaan Israel di utara.

Object of His Ministry: The northern kingdom of Israel.

 

 

Pokok: Tuhan sebagai Keselamatan bagi Orang Israel yang Berzina dan Murtad dalam Menerima Mereka Kembali dan Memulihkan Mereka

Subject of Hosea: Jehovah as Salvation to the Adulterous and Apostate Israel in Receiving Her Back and Restoring Her
